  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "MOTORCYCLE MECHANIC",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>You will service, repair, and maintain motorcycles, focusing on  Aerox, NMAX, Y15, and similar models. Your work will include performing diagnostics, conducting routine maintenance, replacing worn parts, and ensuring motorcycles are safe and fully functional.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform detailed diagnostics on motorcycles to identify mechanical and electrical issues for accurate repairs</li><li>Conduct routine maintenance tasks to keep motorcycles in optimal working condition</li><li>Replace worn or damaged parts to restore motorcycle performance and safety</li><li>Complete full motorcycle overhauls to ensure comprehensive servicing and reliability</li><li>Maintain safety standards by verifying all repairs and maintenance meet functional and safety requirements</li><li>Collaborate with team members to support a friendly and productive work environment</li><li>Demonstrate a positive work attitude and willingness to learn new skills and techniques</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Experience servicing Yamaha Aerox, NMAX, Y15, or similar motorcycle models</li><li>Openness to training and skill development</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><ul><li>Working Location at Kaki Bukit Area.</li><li>Working Hours: 6:30 PM onwards (flexible)</li><li>Compensation: On-time, target/project-based pay</li><li>Location: Eunos</li><li>How to Apply: DM us on Telegram @skgaragee or call/WhatsApp 8847 1296 with your experience and bikes you’ve worked on.</li></ul>",
